Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Casio G-Shock ana/digi canvas strap watch AW-591MS-1AER RRP £110.00 Now £70.00 Description This casually styled Casio G-Shock watch features a black canvas buckle fastened strap, striking black leather look detailing and vibrant orange detailing. Featuring the typical rugged Casio G-Shock black resin casing but in a slightly smaller size than a standard G-Shock, this AW-591MS-1AER Casio watch has a 46mm wide casing. Although slightly smaller in size, this watch is still packed with useful features including a stopwatch, timer, auto LED light and analogue and digital time. The useful auto LED feature mean when activated, the vibrant orange back light can be triggered at just the flick of a wrist in low lighting. The back light can also be manually pressed by one of the function buttons to the side of the watch. The sporty look to the face of the watch is complemented by highlights of orange to the hour markers. The 28mm wide black textured canvas strap is backed with a bright orange reverse completing the designer look. Secured with a buckle fastening, the watch is suitable for wrist sizes 6.5”-9” and the strap is held in place by a black leather look retainer. At 200M water resistant, this Casio AW-591MS-1AER ana/digi watch is suitable for everyday wear and all daily activities.
